# Extracted Debian netinst/DVD reference material that lives at the repo
# root (.disk, boot, dists, pool, install.amd, firmware, EFI, isolinux, ...).
# This is not used by the live-build pipeline (which does its own fresh
# debootstrap during the CI ISO build) and is far too large / contains
# individual files over GitHub's 100MB push limit. Kept on disk locally,
# just not version-controlled.
/.disk/
/boot/
/css/
/dists/
/doc/
/EFI/
/firmware/
/install/
/install.amd/
/isolinux/
/pics/
/pool/
/md5sum.txt
/README.html
/README.mirrors.html
/README.mirrors.txt
/README.source
/README.txt
